Line\">NovoPen Junior<sup>a</sup>, NovoPen 5</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1067573\" data-text=\"Tresiba\"></a>Tresiba (insulin </div><div class=\"tableLine\">degludek)</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">-</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">steady state</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&gt; 24</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">FlexTouch, NovoPen 5</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\"><p>Långverkande insulinanaloger 2-fas</p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1067594\" data-text=\"Ryzodeg\"></a>Ryzodeg (insulin </div><div class=\"tableLine\">degludek, insulin </div><div class=\"tableLine\">aspart)</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">0,25</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">0,5–1,5</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&gt; 24</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">FlexTouch, NovoPen 5</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\"><p><strong>Preparat för kontinuerlig insulinbehandling (insulinpump)<sup>b</sup></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1067615\" data-text=\"Insuman Infusat\"></a>Insuman Infusat <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">(insulin humant)</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">0,5</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1–2</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">5–8</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">–</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"footNotes\"><div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_39\">a. <div class=\"tableLine\">Utgående modell.</div></div><div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_40\">b. <div class=\"tableLine\">Actrapid finns även för kontinuerlig tillförsel. Kortverkande insulinanaloger är också dokumenterade för tillförsel i insulinpump.</div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
